lead_paragraph: England soccer team manager Sam Allardyce has been caught up in a newspaper sting in which he is alleged to have met a bogus consortium of Far East businessmen seeking advice on the Premier League’s billion pound transfer market.

headline.print_headline: England Manager Allardyce Caught in Newspaper Sting
